title: MiddleSex (OprahBookClubPick)
description:
Spanning across eight decades--and one unusually awkward adolescence--Jeffrey Eugenides&#039; long-awaited second novel is a grand, utterly original fable of crossed bloodlines, the intricacies of gender, and the deep, untidy promptings of desire.
The CD edition includes an interview with the Author.
Annotation

Winner of the 2003 Pulitzer Prize for Fiction.
Nominated for the 2002 National Book Critics Circle Award, Fiction.
2002 Lambda Literary Award Finalist, Transgender.
